dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Kenneth Thomas. May I have your name, please?
Hi Kenneth, my name is Evelyn Flores.
Nice to meet you, Evelyn. Can you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Of course, my policy number is five five two three six and my date of birth is zero six one two one nine eight seven.
Thank you, Evelyn. I also need your current address to update our records. Could you please share your street address and ZIP code?
Certainly, my street address is two zero zero Main Street and the ZIP code is three three one zero five.
Thank you for providing that information, Evelyn. Is there anything else you would like to inquire about your policy or any changes you wish to make today?
No, I think that covers everything for now. Thank you.
You're welcome, Evelyn. If you have any further questions in the future, feel free to reach out. Thank you for choosing Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
Thank you, Kenneth. Have a great day too!
